the fiction data set and both unfiltered English data sets. Our findings\nemphasize the need to fully characterize the dynamics of the Google Books\ncorpus before using these data sets to draw broad conclusions about cultural\nand linguistic evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Jan 2015 20:09:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 May 2015 10:11:46 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 24 Mar 2017 11:46:25 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 27 May 2020 13:37:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-28"}
