 protected. We also check proposals for enhanced IR affine E_6\nsymmetries in one such model, verifying that (matching) chiral states in phases\nof corresponding GLSMs transform as 27s, 27^*s.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Jan 2015 21:00:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 13 Jun 2015 00:21:06 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 23 Jun 2015 12:49:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-07"}
