ty $N_H \\sim 10^{25} \\, \\mathrm{cm^{-2}}$\nin the late stages of the simulation. We briefly discuss the observational\nimplications of the model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 5 Jan 2015 21:00:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-05"}
